00:40:24,871 --> 00:40:30,217
The only problem is that you want to maybe filter it quite heavily because of course

680
00:40:30,217 --> 00:40:32,640
you can't really control what goes into that microphone.

681
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:36,324
You know, people may be banging their fingers on it.

682
00:40:37,027 --> 00:40:38,508
But you can sort of cue it.

683
00:40:38,508 --> 00:40:41,590
I think also head motions can help.

