00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:44,612
There are subtle motions that you do with your head

685
00:40:44,612 --> 00:40:46,753
when you breathe.

686
00:40:46,753 --> 00:40:49,635
But it doesn't need to be very enforced.

687
00:40:49,635 --> 00:40:54,337
It's just like a very wispy kind of particle effect

688
00:40:54,337 --> 00:40:56,779
is kind of enough to feel that there's air

689
00:40:56,779 --> 00:40:57,799
coming out of you.

